scenes.description: Mori Calliope explores the 'Story Thus Far' museum, viewing displays for Myth, Promise, and Advent.
Calliope stops at a memorial plaque to thank the map creators, SeafoamBoy and Mmaellon.
Calliope discusses a sense of déjà vu and decides to initiate a flashback to a past performance.
Music video performance of 'FLASH BANG' featuring Mori Calliope, Hakos Baelz, and IRyS.
